{{For|the Greek historian and mythographer|Pherecydes of Leros}}
{{Infobox philosopher
| region           = [[Western philosophy]]
| era              = [[Pre-Socratic philosophy]]
| image   = Pherecydes.jpg
| caption = Pherecydes, ancient Greek philosopher.
| name             = Pherecydes of Syros
| birth_date       = c. 580 BC
| death_date       = c. 520 BC
| school_tradition = [[Pre-Socratic philosophy|Pre-Socratic]]
| main_interests   = [[Cosmogony]], [[mythology]], [[theology]]
